      "text": "まぁそのかわり、美味しく食べれますから～\nちなみに顔は、琴乃ちゃんをイメージして作りました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ at least you can eat this one~.\nBy the way‚ we made the face by imagining Kotono-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 363.3999463398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね、なんかいろいろ振り回しちゃったと思うけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ we kind of put you through a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 367.4999463398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn023.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、嬉しい……。ありがとう、こころ、さくら\nかき氷機も、最初からこのためだったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's okay‚ I’m happy… Thank you‚ Kokoro‚ Sakura.\nSo the shaved ice machine was for this all along.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 379.6666130065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことないですよ？　イタズラにも使いますから\nメロン味とみせかけて、わさび味を食べさせたり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course not! I’m also going to use it for pranks!\nLike‚ pretending it’s melon flavored and giving someone wasabi flavor!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 387.6332796732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn024.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、じゃあそういうことにしておくわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ I’ll take your word for it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 391.9666130065,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-kkr022.m4a",
      "text": "なんなんですか、その生温かい目はー！\nせっかく作った雪だるまが溶けちゃいますよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s with that lukewarm look~!\nThe snowman we worked so hard to make is going to melt!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 400.5332796732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-skr016.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、型に入れて作ったから、すぐまた作れるけどね\nあっ、そうだ！　琴乃ちゃんも作ってみる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahahaha‚ we made it with a mold‚ so we can make another one right away!\nOh‚ that’s right! Kotono-chan‚ do you want to try making one?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 409.2333455403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn025.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、この雪だるまは食べるのもったいないから\nもう少し、冷凍庫に入れとこうかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ this snowman is too precious to eat‚\nso I think I’ll keep it in the freezer for a little longer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 417.2332695006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn026.m4a",
      "text": "（プレゼントありがとう、こころ、さくら）\n（まさか、私の方が驚かされちゃうなんて）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Thank you for the present‚ Kokoro‚ Sakura.）\n（I never thought I’d be the one getting surprised.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 428.533255259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn027.m4a",
      "text": "（クリスマスって、悲しい思い出もあるけど……）\n（二人のおかげで、また一つ、楽しい思い出が増えたわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Christmas… I have some sad memories‚ but…）\n（Thanks to you two‚ I have another happy memory.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 437.8665560402,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_51_03-ktn028.m4a",
      "text": "（直接は、恥ずかしくて言い辛いけど……）\n（これからもよろしくね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It’s embarrassing to say it directly‚ but…）\n（Thank you for being my friend.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 449.3332227068,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}